artists: an array of simple artist objects
href: string	 -  A link to the Web API endpoint providing full details of the track
id: string  -  The Spotify ID for the track
name: string  -  The name of the track
preview_url: string  -  A URL to a 30 second preview (MP3 format) of the track. null if not available
uri: string	 -  The Spotify URI for the track
